Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:41.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:47.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:54.15,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:02:00.60,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:03.97,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.02,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:23.02,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:29.32,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:38.87,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.15,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 好不容易见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT上的人们 都在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感谢克鲁泽队长的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格尼号会负责将您安全送到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯号能赶在悼念仪式前返回吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就非我所能决定的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战果固然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也请不要忘记在战争中牺牲的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与之战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 期待能早日再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与之战斗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克的事听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭…若不除掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个受害者可能就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:52.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1178,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}芙蕾的抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度调头 继续减速20%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整相对速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这样合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大摇大摆停在墨涅拉俄斯号边上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔巴顿提督一定想好好看看这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他老人家还说要上船看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督阁下是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主张研发这艘船和「G」的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说平民去墨涅拉俄斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里转乘穿梭机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着这身 我们也还是平民百姓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于强袭 你有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算 什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船上每个人都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为它的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和驾驶它的人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才得以活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你在想什么 娜塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 基拉不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但他的能力十分宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果轻易…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有能力 我们也无法强迫他入伍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和舰队会合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还这么急着修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏着的话心里不踏实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号称第八舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员里也没几个老鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真出状况 还是得靠上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些 强袭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用改回原来的系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再改回去降低性能也有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人能够继续发挥它的作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 来视察了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 想和基拉说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种怀疑的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己精力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终没机会找你认真聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 很想好好谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段日子难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出各种苛刻要求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你去冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们心存感激
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 别这样…舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家虽然嘴上不说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心底里都在谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然眼下形势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地面上也会很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 他们报告我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯被毁时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为再也见不到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是上天给我的馈赠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说刚才又死里逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好生担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下娜塔尔·巴基露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七轨道舰队 穆·拉·弗拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好在有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在下并未帮上什么大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 他们就是你说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们临时协助舰上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是赫利奥波利斯上的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来时已经替你们打听了家人下落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位马上就能合家团圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常情况下 你们表现的很勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我向你们表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 时间不多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有时间听你们说这一路上的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐格勒号和卡莫夫号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经会合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被察觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力舰队大多已经空降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为他们会去月球总部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来打算将长腿直接送往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空降目标会是阿拉斯加吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尽可能在我们的地盘里围歼它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐格勒号上有六架Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边包括神盾在内有五架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莫夫号上的暴风和迅雷亦可出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睿将哈尔巴顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该是他退出历史舞台的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为这一船一机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致赫利奥波利斯被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还搭上阿尔狄弥斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们保住的这一船一机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或早或晚将造福我地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉斯加似乎不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 他们对宇宙战场了解多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉是我的理解者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁敢挑她们的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个调整人孩子的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也无必要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和为保护他的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故全心全意为我们而战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有他的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐无法抵达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管是形势所迫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对必须与自己同胞战斗的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到十分难过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子为人诚实善良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人认为值得以信赖回报他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 直接释放未免…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕在下僭越进言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与霍夫曼上校持相同意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力有目共睹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为对G系列机密了如指掌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合完全野放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 已经送给扎夫特四架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今有何机密可言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力相当宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下认为应该为我军所用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 从拉米亚斯上尉的话中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他本人没有那个意向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父母都是自然人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自逃离赫利奥波利斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在身在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要军队对其进行保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂就少插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的士兵能有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的事到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在今后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号马上必须
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以现有人员编制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落阿拉斯加本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中霸王…两架？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这不是大气层内用的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送补充兵员的先遣队被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们手头已经没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以分给大天使号的人员了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 赫利奥波利斯被毁后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号和G必须携带所有数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜一切代价返回阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽早让那些东西的开发进入正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特接二连三的投入新机型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群唯利是图的家伙尽造些废铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对前线的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有个数字上的认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必将阁下的一片赤诚之心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保送到阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为机动棺材驾驶员中的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有拒绝的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退伍许可书？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是军人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八舰队 大天使号所属
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 由你事后转交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在战时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民百姓参与战斗也是犯罪行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为避免让那种情况发生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将日期提前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们归入志愿兵的行列了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得保管好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 军务中得知的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在退役之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有参战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没给你准备文件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是为这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿参军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真到走时 又恋恋不舍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 我看过关于你的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 真是让人惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们调整人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为勉强抵御扎夫特机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而制造的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却变成了怪物般的超级兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你父母是自然人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他们出于什么梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你成为调整人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 希望战争尽早结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨涅拉俄斯号唤你速回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 连和你们多聊几句的时间也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你保护了大天使号和强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好的时代到来前 可别死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉她们今后会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号即将去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们还要奔赴下一个战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在为什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 你的能力很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对军队来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但胜负不只取决于你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太自大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们告诉我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是责任的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是你有那意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有强烈意愿的人一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一句胡闹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲死后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔斯塔事务次官的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我叫芙蕾·阿尔斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚得知父亲遇难时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨不得马上离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满心想着这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和舰队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知马上能回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然产生一种疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑问？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的能安心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的能和平了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的战争还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…因为身处中立国一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲他为结束战争付出了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的和平 真正的安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有在战争中赢取…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想 继承父亲的意志战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我的力量 根本不值一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的战争还在继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱跑 小艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大哥哥保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾说的 也是我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 我总不能扔下她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号本来就缺人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以后被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔留下的话 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都留下 我怎么能一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三分钟后机动战士出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 检查系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隔离壁封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了 始终找不到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们让你带上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退伍许可书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才 决定留下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在大天使号 当兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级1 罗拉西亚级2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色18 距离500
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测15分钟后遇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝我们这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 偏偏这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止搬运 封锁管道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨涅拉俄斯号的小艇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催他们赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾志愿参军了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 全员一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边的 要开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 稍等 还有他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地球一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么也别加入扎夫特哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦 快给我引路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架尸装会要你的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上船就快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉用零式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 修完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大哥哥保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下形势
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地面也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那种能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做你能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被托付的不仅是责任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉择的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉获得的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对再次袭来的克鲁泽队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉能做的是保护？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是只有仇恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场无情 炮火再次唤来悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天降之星」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲破呼啸的大气 高达！

